Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.29,0:00:52.29,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cut open my skull look into my head
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.68,0:00:55.17,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why I'm so harsh
