Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:05.67,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:10.64,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never walk alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.41,0:21:10.64,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never walk alone
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:13.31,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,アナタと行く
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:13.31,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你一同走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:19.94,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんな罪も　背負ってあげる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:19.94,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論何種罪孽 願幫你背負
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:32.81,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,道なき道を歩いてくの　アナタと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:32.81,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走向那已路不成路之途
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:37.49,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:37.49,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你一同
